snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' Vs. LSE - FULL WEEK SHOWCASE
snippet.description:
PLAY NOW: https://gamebanana.com/mods/358645

Face off against the guitar man himself in "Vs. LongestSoloEver", a guitar hero Friday Night Funkin' Mod.

CREDITS:

Director / Lead Project Manager / Playtester - Sam H (https://twitter.com/Sam_HOfficial)

Music/Code/Graphic Design/Charting/Voice Acting - LongestSoloEver (https://twitter.com/longestsoloever)

Character Design / Menu & Promotional Art - MarbleInsanity (https://twitter.com/MarbleInsanity)

Background Art - Spacedust (https://twitter.com/BLACK_SPACEDUST)

Mania Mode Remix - iFlicky (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCd_cW1JAfelCjFWX03UAW5w)

Menu Theme - Starbreak (https://www.youtube.com/c/StarbreakMusic)

Charting - Cerbera (https://www.youtube.com/c/Cerberaa)

Charting - Niffirg (https://www.youtube.com/c/niffirg0)

Coding & Events - Serkoid (https://www.youtube.com/c/Serkoid)
